Which class would you use to store your birthday in years, months, days, seconds, and nanoseconds?
	LocalDateTime class
	
Given a random date, how would you find the date of the previous Thursday?
	The previous method of a TemporalAdjuster can be used.
	
What is the difference between a ZoneId and a ZoneOffset?
	Both track an offset from Greenwich/UTC time, but ZoneOffset tracks the absolute offset from Greenwich/UTC. The ZoneId alse uses the ZOneRules to determine how an offset varies for a particular time of year/region.

How would you convert an Instant to a ZonedDateTime? How would you convert a ZonedDateTime to an Instant?
	By using the ZonedDateTime.ofInstant method, a ZoneID must also be supplied.
	
